# BPM Business Rules

## Bookings & Events

- Socials are NOT bookable and do NOT generate penalties
- Weekly events are NOT bookable until confirmed by admin
- Student Practice is provisional — make it configurable
- Only class bookings are subject to penalties and credit deductions

## Role Balancing

Applies to these styles only (configurable list):
Bachata, Bachata Tradicional, Bachata Partnerwork, Cuban, Salsa Line

Each class booking tracks leader/follower role. Waitlist logic is per-role.

## Penalties (classes only)

- Late cancel: €2
- No-show: €5
- No blocking system — penalties are fees, not access restrictions
- Socials are excluded from all penalty logic

## Credits & Attendance

- If a student does not attend a class, attempt to deduct from their class credits/pack
- Socials are excluded from credit deduction

## Memberships & Passes

- Student memberships, packs, and credits are supported
- Promo pass "Beginners 1 and 2": applies to ONE selected style only
- "Beginners Latin Combo": includes two of three Beginner 1 courses — exact mapping is configurable (mark as PROVISIONAL)

## Teachers & Scheduling

- Teacher pairs rotate by slot
- Do NOT hardcode teacher assignment logic — keep it data-driven and configurable
